<NEW>

GRIMLOCK stirred as he looked up his optics darkening, "Me Grimlock
say we smash!" He looked at the other DINOBOTS. "Dinobots destroy
everything!"

There was a nod from SNARL and SLAG, their large heads nodding in
agreement as SNARL swung with his heavy tail at the base of a large
tree! He may not be as large as he once was, but he was still quite
strong.

The tree cracked and splintered and then began to slowly fall across
the center of the clearing they werre all standing in!

BACKSTOP glanced over at WHEELIE as he spoke quietly. "We were trying
to lure them across that bridge." He pointed quietly as the trees that
SWOOP had helped knock down a short while ago. "Once they crossed that
bridge and we knocked it away they would have been trapped on the
other side."

SWOOP nodded sadly as he glanced at GRIMLOCK. "Me swoop only want to help."

Meanwhile the DINOBOTS were turning to make their way back into the
jungle, walking away from the bridge BACKSTOP was talking about and
back into the jungle itself.

"ROOAARR!!!" The trees themselves swayed as GRIMLOCK's voice echoed out!

(TAG)

- Preston
